SEO

Iryna Stepchenkova — 
collection of keywords,
Expansion of the site structure based on the collected semantics
monitoring and analysis of competitors
optimization of website content, including titles, descriptions, headings and internal link structure

Work in WordPress: filling in meta tags, writing and editing page content.

Analysis of positions and traffic
Optimization of the profile in google my business
Setting up Google Ads advertising
Posting to social networks (FB, Instagram, Linkedin, X), Reddit
Work in Apollo - searching and filtering leads, creating and sending emails to potential customers.

1) JavaScript Development:


Emil will primarily work on Google Apps Scripts to develop and enhance the automation functionalities linked to Google Sheets. He may be responsible for API integration and automating various tasks for the client, based on their specific needs.


2) Frontend Development:


The client may also require assistance with frontend tasks for web-based projects. Although the backend work seems secondary, Emil might be involved in frontend logic and interface tasks where necessary.


3) API Integrations & Automation:


Work on integrating various APIs to enhance the client's workflow automation systems, as requested by the client. Help implement automation features to improve project efficiency.


The client will review Emil's expertise and the project scope internally and make final decision.
